<title>USA: Mattson Technology names Martin president.</title>
<headline>Mattson Technology names Martin president.</headline>
<dateline>FREMONT, Calif. 1997-01-27</dateline>
<text>
<p>Mattson Technology Inc on Monday said it has named Ralph Martin, executive vice president and chief operating officer, to the additional post of president.</p>
<p>Martin will continue to report to Brad Mattson, who remains chairman and chief executive officer.</p>
